    "text": "\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0ba8\u0bca\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb0 \u0bb5\u0bc8\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0baa\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0ba9. \u0ba4\u0bae\u0bb2\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bca\u0bb0\u0b95\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bca\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0ba9. Suspect Wanted for Multiple Three-Wheeler Thefts Arrested with Heroin \u2013 Homagama Divisional Criminal Investigation Bureau",
    "fonts": [
      "Kavivanar-Regular",
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "YuGothic-Regular"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      242.08,
      524.77,
      310.56
    ],
    "text": "On the afternoon of 20.04.2026, officers of the Homagama Divisional Criminal Investigation Bureau carried out a raid in the Katuwana area of the Homagama Police Division based on received intelligence. During the operation, a suspect travelling in a three-wheeler was apprehended in possession of 20 grams and 830 milligrams of heroin and subsequently produced before the Homagama Police Station.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      325.12,
      490.3,
      338.4
    ],
    "text": "The suspect is a 29-year-old resident of the Rasnayakepura, Nikaweratiya area.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      352.84,
      518.47,
      393.72
    ],
    "text": "Further inquiries revealed that the suspect was wanted in connection with the theft of four three-wheelers reported within the Homagama, Maharagama, and Maradana Police Divisions.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      408.3,
      486.54,
      435.38
    ],
    "text": "Four stolen three-wheelers have been recovered and taken into police custody. Ongoing investigations are being conducted by the Homagama Police.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
