      505.46
    ],
    "text": "On the morning of 20.04.2026, the Kekirawa Police Station commenced an investigation upon receiving information regarding the discovery of a \u0d2e\u0d43\u0d24\u0d26ad body in the Small Kekirawa Tank within the Kekirawa Police Division.",
